369
00:29:23,050 --> 00:29:24,810
Thank you.

370
00:29:24,810 --> 00:29:26,700
Let's sit then.

371
00:29:32,260 --> 00:29:34,930
First of all, congratulations to everyone who has passed Cayman's

372
00:29:34,930 --> 00:29:36,920
