00:32:12,070 --> 00:32:14,420
Why didn't you thank me then?

404
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:19,710
- You and my cousin...
- Stop!

405
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:21,660
I don't want to talk about him.

406
00:32:25,090 --> 00:32:27,930
Brother Xiaoyu, say,

407
00:32:27,930 --> 00:32:30,880
