408
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:33,130
Not in this lifetime.

409
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:37,690
However, I'm a sensible person.

410
00:32:37,690 --> 00:32:40,720
You will always be my good younger sister.

411
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,250
